---
---

<section class="about section" id="about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-grid">
      <div class="about-content animate-in">
        <span class="section-label">Who We Are</span>
        <h2 class="section-title">A Cultural NGO<br />Rooted in Rajasthan</h2>
        <div class="gold-divider"></div>
        <p class="about-text">
          Actors Theatre Rajasthan (ATR) was founded with a singular belief — that theatre is not 
          mere entertainment. It is a mirror held up to society, a hammer that breaks silence, 
          and a flame that ignites collective consciousness.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          As a registered non-governmental organisation, ATR brings together playwrights, 
          directors, actors, and social activists who collaborate to create performances that 
          address the most pressing issues of our times — from gender equality and child rights 
          to cultural identity and civic responsibility.
        </p>
        <p class="about-text">
          Backed by the <strong>Ministry of Culture, Government of India</strong> and operating 
          in collaboration with Sangeet Natak Akademi, ATR has established itself as one of 
          Rajasthan's most influential theatre organisations.
        </p>

        <div class="about-pillars">
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="22" height="22">
                <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/>
                <path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Cultural Preservation</h4>
              <p>Keeping Rajasthani folk traditions alive through contemporary theatre</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="22" height="22">
                <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/>
                <path d="M12 8v4l3 3"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Social Advocacy</h4>
              <p>Using the stage to raise awareness on gender, rights, and human dignity</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="pillar">
            <div class="pillar-icon">
              <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" width="22" height="22">
                <path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/>
                <circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/>
                <path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h4>Community Building</h4>
              <p>Training the next generation of theatre artists across Rajasthan</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="about-visual animate-in">
        <div class="image-stack">
          <div class="img-main">
            <img 
              src="/images/706930821_4570883119811247_2882408597650510381_n.jpg" 
              alt="Rajrangam festival — Gopichand musical performance on stage" 
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="img-secondary">
            <img 
              src="/images/510981085_10061155840665371_9023389902411716223_n.jpg" 
              alt="Rajrangam national seminar on art, culture and identity" 
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="img-accent">
            <div class="accent-text">
              <span class="accent-num">7th</span>
              <span class="accent-label">Rajrangam<br/>Festival</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    background: var(--section-dark);
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 5rem;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about-text {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.9;
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
  }

  .about-text strong {
    color: var(--ivory);
  }

  .about-pillars {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
    padding-top: 2rem;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
  }

  .pillar {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .pillar-icon {
    width: 44px;
    height: 44px;
    background: rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.08);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: 4px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .pillar h4 {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--ivory);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .pillar p {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Image stack */
  .about-visual {
    position: sticky;
    top: 6rem;
  }

  .image-stack {
    position: relative;
    height: 560px;
  }

  .img-main {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 80%;
    height: 65%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.1);
  }

  .img-main img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .img-main:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.04);
  }

  .img-secondary {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    right: 0;
    width: 65%;
    height: 52%;
    border-radius: 4px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
    border: 1px solid rgba(201, 168, 76, 0.1);
  }

  .img-secondary img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    object-position: center top;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .img-secondary:hover img {
    transform: scale(1.04);
  }

  .img-accent {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 52%;
    left: 78%;
    transform: translate(-50%, 50%);
    width: 90px;
    height: 90px;
    background: var(--crimson);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-direction: column;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 0.5rem;
    z-index: 10;
    border: 3px solid var(--dark-bg);
  }

  .accent-num {
    font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .accent-label {
    font-size: 0.55rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: rgba(250, 246, 239, 0.8);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 3rem;
    }

    .about-visual {
      position: static;
      order: -1;
    }

    .image-stack {
      height: 380px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .image-stack { height: 300px; }
  }
</style>
